  m_Text: 'This game is designed to teach you essential driving habits and traffic
    rules while testing your skills through three engaging challenges:


    Stop
    Sign Challenge: Learn the importance of stopping completely at stop signs to
    ensure safety and avoid accidents at intersections.


    Pedestrian Crosswalk
    Challenge: Practice stopping for pedestrians at crosswalks, respecting their
    right of way, and improving road safety.


    Yield Sign Challenge: Understand
    when and how to yield at intersections to prioritize other vehicles and maintain
    smooth traffic flow.


    "Drive safely, respect the rules, and complete the
    challenges to become a skilled and responsible driver!"'
